%% Data Flow Diagram - ODH Notebook Controller (kubeflow)
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / ODH Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as NotebookWebhook<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS (service-ca)
    participant Controller as ODH Notebook Controller
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS (service-ca)
    participant Notebook as Notebook Container<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant DSPA as DSPA CR
    participant ImageRegistry as OpenShift Image Registry<br/>5000/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,ImageRegistry: Flow 1: Notebook Creation with Auth

    User->>K8sAPI: POST Notebook CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-notebook-v1<br/>Auth: API server webhook auth
    Webhook->>K8sAPI: GET ImageStream tags<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Webhook: ImageStream resolution
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Notebook<br/>(sidecar injected, CA mounted)
    K8sAPI-->>User: Notebook created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute (central ns)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ReferenceGrant (user ns)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create kube-rbac-proxy Service,<br/>SA, ConfigMap, ClusterRoleBinding<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicies<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over User,ImageRegistry: Flow 2: User Accessing Notebook (with auth)

    User->>Gateway: GET /notebook/{ns}/{name}/*<br/>Auth: Browser session
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward request<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS (service-ca)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token forwarded
    KRBP->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Authorized
    KRBP->>Notebook: Proxy request<br/>8888/TCP HTTP plaintext (localhost)<br/>X-Auth-Request-User/Groups headers
    Notebook-->>KRBP: Response
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>User: Response

    Note over User,ImageRegistry: Flow 3: Elyra Pipeline Secret Sync

    Controller->>K8sAPI: GET DSPA CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: DSPA spec/status
    Controller->>K8sAPI: GET Gateway CR (openshift-ingress)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Gateway hostname
    Controller->>K8sAPI: GET S3 credentials Secret<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: S3 credentials
    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE/UPDATE ds-pipeline-config Secret<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
